code link : https://github.com/U7P4L-IN/simple-calculator.git

DOCUMENTATION : Purpose: The program is a basic calculator that performs addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division based on user input.

Input:

Two integers (num1 and num2). An integer (choice) to select the operation. Operations:

Addition: result = num1 + num2 Subtraction: result = num1 - num2 Multiplication: result = num1 * num2 Division: result = (float)num1 / num2 (with error handling for division by zero) Error Handling:

Handles invalid operation choices. Handles division by zero. Exit:

Exits the program when the user selects option 5
